<i>noun</i>: 추구 [추구], 모색 [모색] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>추구 [추구]</dt><br>
<dd>pursuit; seeking</dd><br>
<dd>목적을 이루기 위해 계속 따르며 구함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of following and trying to find something or to achieve one's purpose.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모색 [모색]</dt><br>
<dd>seeking</dd><br>
<dd>일을 해결할 수 있는 방법이나 방향을 깊고 넓게 생각해서 찾음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of finding the direction or solution necessary to solve a problem by thinking broadly and deeply.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>